			******* Aims of the Game. *******

	Reach the right hand side of the level. Avoid spikes and beasties.
	Collect little hearts that are released when enemies die. Collect
	Zool tokens to build up spell power.

			******* Killing Bad guys. *******

	1: Jump on them (a la Robocod)

	2: Shoot them with a bullet (you have a limited supply)

	3: Slice 'n Dice with your sword.

			******* Magic Spells *******

	Collect the Zool tokens to build up spell power. The number of
	charges left is indicated at the bottom of the screen by the 
	little up arrow.

	Casting spells is indicated by a yellow flash. I think you can only
	make Zool leap higher in this demo.

